title: Tues Post Show (6-01-21)
itunes:title: Tues Post Show (6-01-21)
description:
Bobby got an Apple Watch and doesn’t know if he likes it yet. Bobby on having people over to watch the debut of “Breaking Bobby Bones” last night. Raymundo reveals how he got free ammunition for his father-in-law for LIFE! We determined whether or not this person who offered it to him was messing with him. We find out that Mike D’s brother is a tour manager for a punk band. Bobby also explains the World’s First Invisible Sculpture that just sold for $18,000.
